      "widgets_values": [
        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h2><span data-ic=\\\"nodes-installed\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Models &amp; Nodes Used in This Workflow</h2><p>\\n\\n</p><p>This workflow uses <b>Z-Image Turbo</b> (GGUF) with a <b>Qwen-4B</b> text encoder and the <b>Flux VAE</b>. Download all three below — each goes into a different ComfyUI folder.</p><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"GGUF\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #9b59b6\\\"></span>&nbsp;Unet Loader (GGUF)</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><p>Main diffusion model. <b>Create the <code>z-image</code> folder inside <code>diffusion_models</code> if it doesn't exist.</b></p><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/gguf-org/z-image-gguf/resolve/main/z-image-turbo-q4_k_s.gguf?download=true\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">z-image-turbo-q4_k_s.gguf<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">~1.5 GB</span></a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/z-image</div><p>\\n\\n</p><p><span data-ic=\\\"puzzle\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #777777\\\"></span>&nbsp;More quant options: <a href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/gguf-org/z-image-gguf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">z-image-gguf on HuggingFace</a></p><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"CLIP\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #00a6c8\\\"></span>&nbsp;CLIPLoader (GGUF)</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><p>Text encoder — converts your prompt into embeddings for the diffusion model.</p><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Lockout/qwen3-4b-heretic-zimage/resolve/main/qwen-4b-zimage-heretic-q8.gguf?download=true\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">qwen-4b-zimage-heretic-q8.gguf<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">~4 GB</span></a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/text_encoders</div><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"VAE\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #22c55e\\\"></span>&nbsp;Load VAE</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><p>Flux 1 VAE — decodes the model's latent output back into pixels.</p><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">ae.safetensors<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">335 MB</span></a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/vae</div><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><p><span data-ic=\\\"warning-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #eab308\\\"></span>&nbsp;<b>Tip:</b> Each pill opens the download page in a new tab. The folder path under each pill tells you where to save the file.</p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":400,\"height\":200}",
