      "widgets_values": [
        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h2><span data-ic=\\\"nodes-installed\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;SDXL Workflow Guide</h2><p>\\n\\n</p><p>This workflow produces <b>high-detail</b> 1024×1024 images in <i>~20 seconds</i> on a modern GPU. Tweak the highlighted values to experiment:</p><p>\\n\\n</p><p><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 224, 102); color: rgb(26, 26, 26)\\\">CFG 7.5</span> <span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(126, 227, 95); color: rgb(26, 26, 26)\\\">Steps 30</span> <span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(185, 101, 240); color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\">Sampler dpmpp_2m</span></p><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"gear\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Settings</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><table class=\\\"pix-note-grid\\\" style=\\\"--pix-note-grid-border: #3b4754; --pix-note-grid-header-bg: #171717\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th>Parameter</th>\\n      <th>Value</th>\\n      <th>Range</th>\\n    </tr>\\n  </thead>\\n  <tbody>\\n    <tr>\\n      <td>CFG</td>\\n      <td>7.5</td>\\n      <td>4 – 12</td>\\n    </tr>\\n    <tr>\\n      <td>Steps</td>\\n      <td>30</td>\\n      <td>20 – 50</td>\\n    </tr>\\n    <tr>\\n      <td>Seed</td>\\n      <td>random</td>\\n      <td>any int</td>\\n    </tr>\\n    <tr>\\n      <td>Resolution</td>\\n      <td>1024 × 1024</td>\\n      <td>SDXL native</td>\\n    </tr>\\n  </tbody>\\n</table><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"checkmark\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #61d960\\\"></span>&nbsp;Steps</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><ol>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"box\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Load <b>Checkpoint Loader</b> → pick SDXL Base</li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"chip\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #22c5d8\\\"></span>&nbsp;Write your prompt in <b>CLIP Text Encode</b></li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"node-v3\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #b965f0\\\"></span>&nbsp;Wire into <b>KSampler</b></li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"checkmark\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #61d960\\\"></span>&nbsp;Run — the image shows up in <b>Save Image</b></li>\\n</ol><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"file\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Example Prompt</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><pre><code>masterpiece, cinematic portrait, golden hour,\\nultra detailed, 8k resolution, f/1.8 shallow depth\\n</code></pre><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #3b4754\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><p style=\\\"text-align: center\\\"><i>Lower CFG (4–6) = more creative. Higher CFG (8–12) = sticks to prompt.</i></p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":779.1334228515625,\"height\":582.0666442871093,\"backgroundColor\":\"#2e2d34\"}",
