      "widgets_values": [
        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h2><span data-ic=\\\"pixaroma\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Pixaroma Community</h2><p>\\n\\n</p><p>Tutorials, workflows, and updates from the Pixaroma team.<br>Everything lives in one place — pick your favourite:</p><p>\\n\\n</p><h3>Connect</h3><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-yt\\\" href=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Subscribe on YouTube</a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-discord\\\" href=\\\"https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Join the Discord</a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><h3>Resources</h3><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-btn-plain\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://github.com/pixaroma/ComfyUI-Pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">GitHub Repository</a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-btn-plain\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">HuggingFace Profile</a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><h3>Quick Links</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><ul>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"github\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #ffffff\\\"></span>&nbsp;<b>Source:</b> <a href=\\\"https://github.com/pixaroma/ComfyUI-Pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">github.com/pixaroma</a></li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"huggingface\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #facc15\\\"></span>&nbsp;<b>Models:</b> <a href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">huggingface.co/pixaroma</a></li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"question\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #22c5d8\\\"></span>&nbsp;<b>Help:</b> open an <a href=\\\"https://github.com/pixaroma/ComfyUI-Pixaroma/issues\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">issue on GitHub</a></li>\\n</ul><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><p style=\\\"text-align: center\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"><b><i>Thank you for using Pixaroma nodes!</i></b></span></p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":401.81818181818153,\"height\":395.7576127485794,\"backgroundColor\":\"#0f1f1e\"}",
